&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>TypeError Class advice impossible in Python3</title><link>https://finisky.github.io/en/class-advice-impossible/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2020 18:52:52 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://finisky.github.io/en/class-advice-impossible/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The error looks like this:&lt;/p&gt;

